        public static final int lookupISA(int nFamily,
                                  int nMajor)
                           throws ScriptingException
        Lookup the ISA that corresponds to a particular family ID and major ISA revision.
        Parameters:
        nFamily - numeric ID of the Family
        nMajor - numeric major revision of the ISA
        Returns:
        ISA corresponding to nFamily and nMajor (e.g. ISA.C64 for Family.TMS320 and 0x64).
        Throws:
        ScriptingException
